<p class="line" data-aid="144619209" id="note3_p6">At home or abroad, on the land or the sea&#xFEFF;&#x2014;</p>
<p class="line" data-aid="144619212" id="note3_p7">As thy days may demand, &#x2026; so thy succor shall be.</p>
</div>
