<p class="line" data-aid="144619223" id="note3_p11">I&#x2019;ll strengthen thee, help thee, and cause thee to stand,</p>
<p class="line" data-aid="144619225" id="note3_p12">Upheld by my righteous, &#x2026; omnipotent hand.</p>
</div>
<div class="stanza">
